object.customQuery:
SELECT lim.Value as Value, Cov.SystemId as SystemId, cov.ParentId as ParentId, Cov.CoverageCd as CoverageCd 
FROM `Limit` lim 
join advrxxchangedbeans advr
on lim.systemid = advr.systemid
and lim.cmmcontainer = advr.cmmcontainer
join Coverage cov
on lim.ParentId=cov.Id
and lim.SystemId=cov.SystemId
Where lim.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
and cov.CMMContainer='Policy'
and LimitCD = 'Limit1'
and CoverageCd in ('CovE','LPL','BIUOC', 'PUCov')

SELECT Coverage.FinalPremiumAmt as FinalPremiumAmt, Coverage.CMMContainer as CMMContainer, Coverage.Id as Id, Coverage.Status as Status, Coverage.SystemId as SystemId, Coverage.CoverageCd as CoverageCd, Coverage.ParentId as ParentId 
FROM Coverage
join advrxxchangedbeans advr
on coverage.systemid = advr.systemid
and coverage.cmmcontainer = advr.cmmcontainer
Where Coverage.CMMContainer='Policy'
and Coverage.Status='Active'

SELECT lim.Value as Value, Cov.SystemId as SystemId, cov.ParentId as ParentId, Cov.CoverageCd as CoverageCd 
FROM `Limit` lim 
join advrxxchangedbeans advr
on lim.systemid = advr.systemid
and lim.cmmcontainer = advr.cmmcontainer
join Coverage cov
on lim.ParentId=cov.Id
and lim.SystemId=cov.SystemId
Where lim.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
and cov.CMMContainer='Policy'
and LimitCD = 'Limit1'
and Status = 'Active'
and CoverageCd in ('CovB','CovB2','CovD', 'HO0448','BIUOC')

SELECT Line.ParentId as ParentId, Line.CMMContainer as CMMContainer, Line.CommercialLiabilityLimit as CommercialLiabilityLimit, Line.CyberLiabilityLimit as CyberLiabilityLimit, Line.PersonalLiabilityLimit as PersonalLiabilityLimit, Line.TotMotOwnLeasBus as TotMotOwnLeasBus, Line.NumMotExcUmb as NumMotExcUmb, Line.NumOwnedAutos as NumOwnedAutos, Line.FullTermAmt as FullTermAmt, Line.NumOfYouthInexp as NumOfYouthInexp, Line.RejectExcessUninsuredMotorists as RejectExcessUninsuredMotorists, Line.NumOfBoatsInbOut as NumOfBoatsInbOut, Line.NumOfAddlBoatsOver150HP as NumOfAddlBoatsOver150HP, Line.NumOfFamilyResTwo as NumOfFamilyResTwo, Line.NumOfFamilyResTwoOffPre as NumOfFamilyResTwoOffPre, Line.NumOfCondoUnits as NumOfCondoUnits, Line.NumOfAddlCondoUnits as NumOfAddlCondoUnits, Line.PrimaryUnderlyingPolNum as PrimaryUnderlyingPolNum, Line.UnderAutLiabPerOcc as UnderAutLiabPerOcc, Line.NumOfAddlBoatsInbOut as NumOfAddlBoatsInbOut, Line.NumOfBoatsOver150HP as NumOfBoatsOver150HP, Line.TerritoryCd as TerritoryCd, Line.SystemId as SystemId, Line.Id as Id 
FROM Line
where CMMContainer = 'Policy'

select u.systemid as SystemId, 
u.idref as IdRef, 
b.effectivedt as EffectiveDt, 
b.expirationdt as ExpirationDt 
from umbrellapolicyinfo u
join basicpolicy b
on u.systemid = b.systemid
and u.cmmcontainer = b.cmmcontainer
where u.cmmcontainer = 'Policy'
order by u.idref asc, u.systemid desc
##

SELECT location.UnderlyingPolicyNumber as UnderlyingPolicyNumber, location.UnderlyingPolicyEffectiveDt as UnderlyingPolicyEffectiveDt, location.UnderlyingPolicyExpirationDt as UnderlyingPolicyExpirationDt, location.SystemId as SystemId, location.Id as Id FROM location
where CMMContainer = 'Policy'

SELECT addr.Addr1 as Addr1, addr.Addr2 as Addr2, addr.Addr3 as Addr3, addr.Addr4 as Addr4, addr.Latitude as Latitude, addr.Longitude as Longitude, addr.SystemId as SystemId, addr.ParentId as ParentId 
,addr.County as County, addr.City as City, addr.PostalCode as PostalCode
,addr.StateProvCd as StateProvCd
FROM addr
join advrxxchangedbeans advr
on addr.systemid = advr.systemid
and addr.cmmcontainer = advr.cmmcontainer
where addr.AddrTypeCd = 'LocationAddr' and addr.CMMContainer = 'Policy'

SELECT basicpolicy.SystemId as SystemId, basicpolicy.PolicyNumber as PolicyNumber, basicpolicy.EffectiveDt as EffectiveDt, basicpolicy.ExpirationDt as ExpirationDt FROM basicpolicy
where CMMContainer = 'Policy'

SELECT basicpolicy.SystemId as SystemId, 
right(basicpolicy.PolicyNumber, 7) as PolicyNumber, 
basicpolicy.EffectiveDt as EffectiveDt, 
basicpolicy.ExpirationDt as ExpirationDt 
FROM basicpolicy
where cmmcontainer = 'Policy'
and description <> 'Personal Umbrella Liability'

object.customQuery:
SELECT Coverage.SystemId as SystemId,
	   Coverage.ParentId as ParentId, 
	   Coverage.CoverageCd as CoverageCd
  FROM Coverage
join advrxxchangedbeans advr
on coverage.systemid = advr.systemid
and coverage.cmmcontainer = advr.cmmcontainer
 WHERE Coverage.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
   AND Coverage.CoverageCd IN ('EQ','HO0454')
   and Coverage.Status = 'Active'

SELECT location.LocationNumber as LocationNumber,
       location.UnderlyingPDOccurrenceLimit as UnderlyingPDOccurrenceLimit,
       location.SystemId as SystemId,
       location.Id as Id,
       CASE when Isnull(location.RiskDefinitionReview) THEN 'N/A'
    ELSE location.RiskDefinitionReview END as RiskDefinitionReview,
       location.RiskDefinitionNotes as RiskDefinitionNotes 
FROM location
WHERE CMMContainer ='Policy'
ORDER BY  location.SystemId,
       location.Id

SELECT Building.CMMContainer as CMMContainer, Building.TerritoryCd as TerritoryCd, Building.SystemId as SystemId FROM Building
where CMMContainer = 'Policy'

SELECT addr.Addr1 as Addr1, addr.Addr2 as Addr2, addr.Addr3 as Addr3, addr.Addr4 as Addr4, addr.County as County, addr.City as City, addr.PostalCode as PostalCode, addr.StateProvCd as StateProvCd, addr.Latitude as Latitude, addr.Longitude as Longitude, addr.SystemId as SystemId, addr.ParentId as ParentId FROM addr
where addr.AddrTypeCd = 'LocationAddr' and addr.CMMContainer = 'Policy'

SELECT location.Id as Id, location.SystemId as SystemId FROM location
where CMMContainer = 'Policy'
and Status = 'Active'

A.WaterLossDed as WaterLossDed,
A.AllPerilDed as AllPerilDed,
A.SystemId as SystemId, 
A.ParentId as ParentId 
FROM (
    SELECT 
        Building.CMMContainer as CMMContainer, 
        Building.Id as Id, 
        Building.BldgNumber as BldgNumber, 
        Building.Status as Status, 
        Building.ConstructionCd as ConstructionCd, 
        Building.YearBuilt as YearBuilt, 
        Building.Units as Units, 
        Building.OccupancyCd as OccupancyCd, 
        Building.InspectionDt as InspectionDt, 
        Building.ProtectionClass as ProtectionClass, 
        Building.TerritoryCd as TerritoryCd, 
        Building.BuildingLimit as BuildingLimit, 
        Building.ContentsLimit as ContentsLimit, 
        Building.BuildingWindHailDeductible as BuildingWindHailDeductible, 
        Building.CovALimit as CovALimit, 
        Building.CovCLimit as CovCLimit, 
        Building.HomeAutoCreditInd as HomeAutoCreditInd, 
        Building.IdentityRecoveryInd as IdentityRecoveryInd, 
        Building.BuildingClassDescription as BuildingClassDescription, 
        Building.ContentClassDescription as ContentClassDescription, 
        Building.NumOfFamilies as NumOfFamilies, 
        Building.SprinklerSystem as SprinklerSystem, 
        Building.StandardDed as StandardDed, 
        Building.PremisesLiability as PremisesLiability, 
        Building.BuildingClass as BuildingClass, 
        Building.ContentsClass as ContentsClass, 
        Building.NumOfApartmentCondoBuilding as NumOfApartmentCondoBuilding, 
        Building.DemolitionLimit as DemolitionLimit, 
        Building.IncreasedCostConstructionLimit as IncreasedCostConstructionLimit, 
        Building.CombDemolitionIncCostLimit as CombDemolitionIncCostLimit, 
        Building.ExpenseMod as ExpenseMod, 
        Building.IndividualRiskPremiumMod as IndividualRiskPremiumMod, 
        Building.DistanceToShore as DistanceToShore, 
        Building.Elevation as Elevation, 
        Building.FloodZone as FloodZone, 
        Building.SIRCoastline as SIRCoastline, 
        Building.CyberLiabilityLimit as CyberLiabilityLimit, 
        Building.AgeCredit as AgeCredit, 
        Building.DUPCCredit as DUPCCredit, 
        CASE
            WHEN DistanceToShore LIKE 'More Than 10 Miles%' THEN 10 
            WHEN DistanceToShore LIKE '%Mile%' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(DistanceToShore, INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') + 2, INSTR(DistanceToShore, 'M') - INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2))
            WHEN DistanceToShore LIKE '%Mi' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(DistanceToShore, INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') + 2, INSTR(DistanceToShore, 'M') - INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2))
            WHEN DistanceToShore LIKE '%mi' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(DistanceToShore, INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') + 2, INSTR(DistanceToShore, 'm') - INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2))
            WHEN DistanceToShore LIKE '%Feet%' THEN
                CONVERT(CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(DistanceToShore, INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') + 2, INSTR(DistanceToShore, 'F') - INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2)) * 0.000189394, DECIMAL(10, 2))
            ELSE NULL 
        END as DistanceToCoastMile,
        CASE 
            WHEN DistanceToShore LIKE 'More Than 10 Miles%' THEN 10 * 5280
            WHEN DistanceToShore LIKE '%Mile%' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(DistanceToShore, INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') + 2, INSTR(DistanceToShore, 'M') - INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2)) * 5280
            WHEN DistanceToShore LIKE '%Mi' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(DistanceToShore, INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') + 2, INSTR(DistanceToShore, 'M') - INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2)) * 5280
            WHEN DistanceToShore LIKE '%mi' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(DistanceToShore, INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') + 2, INSTR(DistanceToShore, 'm') - INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2)) * 5280
            WHEN DistanceToShore LIKE '%Feet%' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(DistanceToShore, INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') + 2, INSTR(DistanceToShore, 'F') - INSTR(DistanceToShore, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2))
            ELSE NULL 
        END as DistanceToCoastFeet,
        CASE 
            WHEN SIRCoastline LIKE 'More Than 10 Miles%' THEN 10  
            WHEN SIRCoastline LIKE '%Mile%' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(SIRCoastline, INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') + 2, INSTR(SIRCoastline, 'M') - INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2)) 
            WHEN SIRCoastline LIKE '%Mi' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(SIRCoastline, INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') + 2, INSTR(SIRCoastline, 'M') - INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2))
            WHEN SIRCoastline LIKE '%mi' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(SIRCoastline, INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') + 2, INSTR(SIRCoastline, 'm') - INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2))
            WHEN SIRCoastline LIKE '%Feet%' THEN
                CONVERT(CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(SIRCoastline, INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') + 2, INSTR(SIRCoastline, 'F') - INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2)) * 0.000189394, DECIMAL(10, 2))
            ELSE NULL 
        END as SIRCoastlineMile,
        CASE 
            WHEN SIRCoastline LIKE 'More Than 10 Miles%' THEN 10 * 5280
            WHEN SIRCoastline LIKE '%Mile%' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(SIRCoastline, INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') + 2, INSTR(SIRCoastline, 'M') - INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2)) * 5280
            WHEN SIRCoastline LIKE '%Mi' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(SIRCoastline, INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') + 2, INSTR(SIRCoastline, 'M') - INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2)) * 5280
            WHEN SIRCoastline LIKE '%mi' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(SIRCoastline, INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') + 2, INSTR(SIRCoastline, 'm') - INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2)) * 5280
            WHEN SIRCoastline LIKE '%Feet%' THEN
                CONVERT(LTRIM(RTRIM(SUBSTRING(SIRCoastline, INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') + 2, INSTR(SIRCoastline, 'F') - INSTR(SIRCoastline, '-') - 3))), DECIMAL(10, 2))
            ELSE NULL 
        END as SIRCoastlineFeet,
        Building.OnPremisesLimit as OnPremisesLimit, 
        Building.OffPremisesLimit as OffPremisesLimit,
        Building.ValuablePapersRecords as ValuablePapersRecords,
        Building.FoodSpoilageLimit as FoodSpoilageLimit, 
        Building.FungiProperty as FungiProperty,

        Building.ExtBuildingFloodLimit as ExtBuildingFloodLimit,
        Building.ExteriorSignsLimit as ExteriorSignsLimit,

        Building.EarthquakeInd as EarthquakeInd,
        Building.BlanketBasisInd as BlanketBasisInd,
        Building.NumOfApartmentCondo as NumOfApartmentCondo,
        Building.Stories as Stories, 
        Building.SqFt as SqFt,
        Building.BuildingAgreedValue as BuildingAgreedValue,
        Building.CovBLimit as CovBLimit,
        Building.CovDLimit as CovDLimit,
        Building.AddAltOtherResLimit as AddAltOtherResLimit,
        Building.ho4IncreasedLimit as ho4IncreasedLimit,
        Building.BusinessPropertyIncLmts as BusinessPropertyIncLmts,
        Building.NotInCovBIncBusLimit as NotInCovBIncBusLimit,
        Building.PrimaryResidence as PrimaryResidence, 
        Building.OtherResidence as OtherResidence, 
        Building.NotInCovBOnPremLimit as NotInCovBOnPremLimit,
        Building.NotInCovBoffPremLimit as NotInCovBoffPremLimit,
        Building.PersonalPropOtherLimit as PersonalPropOtherLimit,
        Building.InCovBNumStructuresAddlLimit as InCovBNumStructuresAddlLimit, 
        Building.IncrPersonalPropStoreLimit as IncrPersonalPropStoreLimit,
        Building.OtherStructures as OtherStructures,
        Building.OtherStructuresIncreaseLimit as OtherStructuresIncreaseLimit,
        Building.RentalValue as RentalValue,
        Building.RentalValueIncreasedLimit as RentalValueIncreasedLimit,
        Building.AdditionalLivingExpenseLimit as AdditionalLivingExpenseLimit,
        Building.BroadTheftOnPremisesLimit as BroadTheftOnPremisesLimit,
        Building.BroadTheftOffPremisesLimit as BroadTheftOffPremisesLimit, 
        Building.BuildingItemsLimit as BuildingItemsLimit,
        Building.EQDeductible as EQDeductible,
        Building.OptionalDed as OptionalDed,
        Building.NumOfBuildingsComplex as NumOfBuildingsComplex,
        Building.ElitePackageInd as ElitePackageInd,
        Building.FireDistrict as FireDistrict,
        Building.OptionalDedType as OptionalDedType,
        Building.IceDamageDed as IceDamageDed,
        Building.WaterLossDed as WaterLossDed,
        Building.AllPerilDed as AllPerilDed,
        Building.SystemId as SystemId, 
        Building.ParentId as ParentId 
    FROM Building
    JOIN advrxxchangedbeans
    ON Building.SystemId = advrxxchangedbeans.SystemId
    AND Building.CMMContainer = advrxxchangedbeans.CMMContainer
    WHERE Building.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
) A
ORDER BY 
    SystemId, ParentId, BldgNumber, Status, ConstructionCd, YearBuilt, Units, OccupancyCd, 
    InspectionDt, ProtectionClass, TerritoryCd, BuildingLimit, ContentsLimit, BuildingWindHailDeductible, 
    CovALimit, CovCLimit, HomeAutoCreditInd, IdentityRecoveryInd, BuildingClassDescription, 
    ContentClassDescription, NumOfFamilies, SprinklerSystem, StandardDed, PremisesLiability, 
    BuildingClass, ContentsClass, NumOfApartmentCondoBuilding, DemolitionLimit, IncreasedCostConstructionLimit, 
    CombDemolitionIncCostLimit, ExpenseMod, IndividualRiskPremiumMod, DistanceToShore, Elevation, FloodZone, 
    SIRCoastline, CyberLiabilityLimit, AgeCredit, DUPCCredit, DistanceToCoastMile, DistanceToCoastFeet, 
    SIRCoastlineMile, SIRCoastlineFeet, OnPremisesLimit, OffPremisesLimit, ValuablePapersRecords, 
    FoodSpoilageLimit, FungiProperty, ExtBuildingBroadLimit, ExtBuildingEQLimit, ExtBuildingFloodLimit, 
    ExteriorSignsLimit, WaterBackupLimit, EarthquakeInd, BlanketBasisInd, NumOfApartmentCondo, 
    Stories, SqFt, BuildingAgreedValue, CovBLimit, CovDLimit, AddAltOtherResLimit, ho4IncreasedLimit, 
    NotInCovBIncBusLimit, PrimaryResidence, OtherResidence, NotInCovBOnPremLimit, NotInCovBoffPremLimit, 
    PersonalPropOtherLimit, InCovBNumStructuresAddlLimit, IncrPersonalPropStoreLimit, OtherStructures, 
    OtherStructuresIncreaseLimit, RentalValue, RentalValueIncreasedLimit, BroadTheftOnPremisesLimit, 
    BroadTheftOffPremisesLimit, BuildingItemsLimit, EQDeductible, OptionalDed, NumOfBuildingsComplex, 
    ElitePackageInd, FireDistrict, OptionalDedType, IceDamageDed, WaterLossDed, AllPerilDed --

select plcy.PolicyNumber as PolicyNumber,ad.StateProvCd as StateProvCd, ad.County as County, ad.City as City, ad.PostalCode as PostalCode from
(
select PolicyNumber,min(SystemId) as SystemId
from basicpolicy where cmmcontainer='Policy' 
 and shellpolicyind is null
  group by PolicyNumber
 )plcy


 inner join basicpolicy bp

 on plcy.PolicyNumber = bp.PolicyNumber

 and bp.CMMContainer = 'Policy'

 and bp.ShellPolicyInd = 'true'

 inner join advrxxchangedbeans advr

 on bp.SystemId = advr.SystemId

 and bp.CMMContainer = advr.CMMContainer

 inner join Risk rk
 on plcy.SystemId=rk.SystemId
 and rk.CmmContainer='Policy'

 and (rk.TypeCd like '%Property%' or rk.Description like '%Primary%')

 inner join Building b
 on rk.Systemid=b.systemId
 and rk.id=b.parentid
 and b.CmmContainer='Policy'
 inner join Addr ad
 on ad.Systemid=plcy.Systemid
 and ad.ParentId=b.id
 and ad.Cmmcontainer='Policy'
 and ad.AddrTypeCd ='RiskAddr'
 ORDER BY PolicyNumber,StateProvCd,County,City,PostalCode --

transformations.description: This is a helper expression for EXP_Anchor11, used to resolve the name conflicts.
transformations.name: _EXPR_EXP_Anchor11

fields.name: v_NumOfStoriesBand
fields.expression:
decode(true,
isnull(v_NumOfStories),'',
ltrim(rtrim(v_NumOfStories)) = '', '',
v_NumOfStories = '.75', '1',
v_NumOfStories = '015', '1.5',
v_NumOfStories = '1 1/2', '1.5',
v_NumOfStories = '2 1/2', '2.5',
v_NumOfStories = '2,5', '2.5',
TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories) = 0, '0',
TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) >= 1.0 and TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) <= 1.4, '1',
TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) = 1.5, '1.5',
TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) >= 1.6 and TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) <= 2.4, '2',
TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) = 2.5, '2.5',
TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) >= 2.6 and TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) <= 3.4, '3',
TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) = 3.5, '3.5',
TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) >= 3.6 and TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) <= 4.4, '4',
TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) >= 4.6 and TO_DECIMAL(v_NumOfStories, 1) <= 5.4, '5',
'6+')

fields.name: UnderlyingAddress
fields.expression: UnderlyingAddr1 || IIF(ISNULL(UnderlyingAddr2), NULL, ' ' || UnderlyingAddr2) || IIF(ISNULL(UnderlyingAddr3), NULL, ' ' || UnderlyingAddr3) || IIF(ISNULL(UnderlyingAddr4), NULL, ' ' || UnderlyingAddr4)

fields.name: PerUnitDeductibleAmt
fields.expression:
IIF(ISNULL(IceDamageDed) = 0, IceDamageDed,
IIF(ISNULL(WaterLossDed) = 0, WaterLossDed,
IIF(ISNULL(AllPerilDed) = 0, AllPerilDed, NULL)))

fields.name: v_CovD_HP_Cond_Limit
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,

transformations.description: This Lookup is used to calculate Earthquake Building Deductible
transformations.name: lkp_policystats_EQbldgDeductanble

object.customQuery:
select 
 Deductible1 as Deductible1,
 PolicyNumber as PolicyNumber,
 LocationNumber as LocationNumber,
 BuildingNumber as BuildingNumber  from (
SELECT PolicyStats_Stg.RateAreaName as RateAreaName, 
       PolicyStats_Stg.Deductible1 as Deductible1, 
	   PolicyStats_Stg.PolicyNumber+PolicyStats_Stg.PolicyVersion as PolicyNumber, 
	   cast(substring(PolicyStats_Stg.riskcd,1,3) as integer) as LocationNumber, 
	   cast(substring(PolicyStats_Stg.riskcd,4,3) as integer) as BuildingNumber,
Row_number() over(partition by PolicyStats_Stg.PolicyNumber+PolicyStats_Stg.PolicyVersion, cast(PolicyStats_Stg.Riskcd as integer)
	   order by PolicyStats_Stg.SystemId desc) rn
FROM dbo.PolicyStats_Stg
where ((lower(replace(PolicyStats_Stg.ProductName,' ','')) in ('businessowners','commercialumbrella')
 and PolicyStats_Stg.RateAreaName ='EarthquakeBuilding')
 or ((lower(replace(PolicyStats_Stg.ProductName,' ','')) = 'dwellingproperty'
 and PolicyStats_Stg.RateAreaName='EQ-CovA')
 or (lower(replace(PolicyStats_Stg.ProductName,' ','')) = 'homeowners')
 and PolicyStats_Stg.RateAreaName='EQ-CovA')) 
 )t
where rn=1
